The paper deals with visual object recognition, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes and evaluates machine learning techniques to improve the effectiveness of convolutional networks, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of regularization techniques, which is a common topic in natural language processing (cs.CL).
